SMB network recurses

Win32API::Net

use Win32::NetResource;

$ShareInfo = {
                &#39;path&#39; =&gt; &quot;C:\\MyShareDir&quot;,
                &#39;netname&#39; =&gt; &quot;MyShare&quot;,
                &#39;remark&#39; =&gt; &quot;It is good to share&quot;,
                &#39;passwd&#39; =&gt; &quot;&quot;,
                &#39;current-users&#39; =&gt;0,
                &#39;permissions&#39; =&gt; 0,
                &#39;maxusers&#39; =&gt; -1,
                &#39;type&#39;  =&gt; 0,
                };

Win32::NetResource::NetShareAdd( $ShareInfo,$parm )
    or die &quot;unable to add share&quot;;

Sending mouse and keyboard events

Win32API::GUItest

use Win32::GuiTest qw(FindWindowLike GetWindowText 
  SetForegroundWindow SendKeys);

$Win32::GuiTest::debug = 0; # Set to &quot;1&quot; to enable verbose mode

my @windows = FindWindowLike(0, &quot;^Microsoft Excel&quot;, &quot;^XLMAIN\$&quot;);
for (@windows) {
    print &quot;$_&gt;\t&#39;&quot;, GetWindowText($_), &quot;&#39;\n&quot;;
    SetForegroundWindow($_);
    SendKeys(&quot;%fn~a{TAB}b{TAB}{BS}{DOWN}&quot;);
}
